g","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2928,"height":1648,"file_path":"/i0sLUCO3R9uMMLY2CeFea2fJzrB.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/1fuYzY7qrvho9BIo1NMc3OS12DU.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/cPJ4xt5ccBJX4BIISyHGCGL52H3.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1300,"height":730,"file_path":"/wb0sWqUGSTx5djJFbY0QqbjsQAH.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.781,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":720,"file_path":"/emyv1d59Al72JfnFYVEboIMkaYD.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":1312,"height":738,"file_path":"/8QbxuVIljFhJYN8q7bIVPHmSjOP.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":2673,"height":1504,"file_path":"/wwC6ylDpH98FdEIu0byfRnz5w9g.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.777,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":721,"file_path":"/js3FCTqQCIRB4I0KNu0mKtBlm8j.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.775,"vote_average":0},{"width":1280,"height":721,"file_path":"/9tpO1jmQzONMIvJ55Nft0DiL3Hm.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.775,"vote_average":0},{"width":3600,"height":2025,"file_path":"/sU5Zv8OzU2UdtkBrviwKTksJTUy.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3600,"height":2025,"file_path":"/u7hKC9niITGlJs3iQkzjlwRgwLO.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":null,"enrichment_cycle":0,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":148,"tagline":"There can be no understanding between the hands and the brain unless the heart acts as mediator.","homepage":"","overview":"In a futuristic city sharply divided between the rich and the poor, the son of the city's mastermind meets a prophet who predicts the coming of a savior to mediate their differences."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":153,"tagline":"Mittler zwischen Hirn und Händen muss das Herz sein.","homepage":"","overview":"Johann Fredersen, ein Großindustrieller, herrscht über die Stadt Metropolis. Dort leben, gespalten in einer Zweiklassengesellschaft, die feinen Herren hoch oben in Hochhäusern, die Arbeiter hingegen tief unter der Erde. Eines Tages taucht Maria, die Heldin der Unterstadt, in den Spielwiesen der Reichen auf und fordert die Befreiung der unterdrückten Arbeiter. Freder, der Sohn des Herrschers, verliebt sich in sie. Der Erfinder Rotwang wird von Freders Vater Johann sodann beauftragt einem Roboter das Aussehen Marias zu geben. Die Roboter-Maria soll die Arbeiter aufstacheln, damit das Establishment noch härter durchgreifen kann. Der Plan hat Erfolg."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Metropolis","runtime":150,"tagline":"Non ci può essere comprensione tra le mani e il cervello a meno che il cuore non agisca da mediatore.","homepage":"","overview":"Nel 2026 in una megalopoli a due livelli gli operai che lavorano come schiavi nei sotterranei sono incitati alla rivolta da un robot femmineo che riproduce le fattezze di una di loro, la mite e pia Maria. L'ha costruito uno scienziato al servizio dei padroni che vuole vendicarsi del potente John Fredersen, dominatore della città. La rivolta provoca un'inondazione che colpisce i quartieri operai finché, sollecitato da Maria, Freder, figlio di Fredersen, fa da mediatore tra padroni e operai. È nato un nuovo patto sociale. Realizzato nel 1926 a costi così alti che rischiarono di far fallire la UFA, fu proiettato a Berlino il 10-1-1927. Ne esistono varie copie, ciascuna diversa dall'altra per durata e montaggio."},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":153,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Handlingen i denna stumfilm utspelar sig runt år 2000. En gigantisk stad styrs med supereffektivitet av industrialisten Jon Fredersen (Alfred Abel) och tycks på ytan vara en utopisk dröm av förmögna invånare i palatsliknande lägenheter i kolossala torn av stål och glas. Under jordytan är det en helt annan historia - arméer av slavar som jobbar oändliga skift för att bibehålla den lyxliknande tillvaron deras mästare åtnjuter."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":150,"tagline":"Il ne peut y avoir de compréhension entre les mains et le cerveau que si le cœur agit comme médiateur.","homepage":"","overview":"En 2026, une métropole à l’architecture fantastique vit sous le joug d’un groupe de tyrans. Les aristocrates se prélassent et se divertissent dans de somptueuses demeures et de luxuriants jardins, tandis que la grande masse de la population travaille, dort et survit durement dans les profondeurs de la terre. Le fils du maître de la ville découvre avec effarement l’existence du monde souterrain, où se rencontrent en secret les ouvriers, peu enclins à supporter pour toujours leur situation. Pendant ce temps, un savant invente une femme‐robot qui doit détourner les opprimés de leur révolte…"},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"Metrópolis","runtime":153,"tagline":"No puede haber acuerdo entre las manos y el cerebro a menos que el corazón actúe como mediador.","homepage":"","overview":"En una megalópolis del año 2000, los obreros están condenados a vivir recluidos en un gueto subterráneo, donde se encuentra el corazón industrial de la ciudad. Sin embargo, incitados por un robot, se rebelan contra la clase dominante y amenazan con destruir la ciudad exterior. Freder (Gustav Frölich), el hijo del soberano de Metrópolis, y María, una muchacha de origen humilde, intentarán evitar la destrucción apelando a los sentimientos y al amor."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":123,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"No futuro, a sociedade de Metropolis está dividida em dois grupos: os trabalhadores,que vivem debaixo da terra e fazem as máquinas funcionar e a classe dominante que vive à suprefície. Os trabalhadores são dirigidos por Maria que quer encontrar um mediador entre a classe dominante e os trabalhadores, pois ela acredita que entre o cérebro e os músculos é necessário um coração. Maria encontra Freder Fredersen, o filho do senhor de Metropolis, Joh Fredersen e apaixonam-se. Entretanto, Joh decide que os trabalhadores já não são necessários a Metropolis e usa um robô para fingir que é Maria e fomentar a revolução entre a classe trabalhadora para a eliminar."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"PT","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Метрополис","runtime":145,"tagline":"«Не может быть взаимопонимания между руками и мозгом, если сердце не выступает в качестве посредника»","homepage":"","overview":"Метрополис — город будущего, разделен на две части. Под землей находятся жилища рабочих, над ними цеха с машинами. В верхнем городе расположены офисы, богатые кварталы и сады развлечений. Вся власть в городе принадлежит магнату Иогану Фендерсону. Его сын — Фредер догадывается о несправедливости, царящей в метрополисе. Спустившись в машинную зону, Фредер приходит в ужас: он видит страшного Молоха, пожирающего людей. Не в силах смириться с увиденным, он начинает борьбу со злом."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"大都会","runtime":153,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"这部1927年的鸿篇巨制或许堪称默片时代的巅峰成就，弗里茨·朗将二十年代通俗小说狂热的叙事节奏，与自身对人性幽暗面的深刻洞察熔铸一体。[Kino International]"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":153,"tagline":"Nie może być porozumienia między rękami i mózgiem, jeśli serce nie będzie pełnić roli mediatora.","homepage":"","overview":"Przyszłość. Ludzie są podzieleni na dwie grupy: myślicieli, którzy stwarzają plany (ale nie wiedzą jak wszystko działa), oraz robotników, którzy wytwarzają (ale nie mają żadnej wizji). Są od siebie kompletnie odseparowani, ale razem tworzą jednak całość. Jeden człowiek z grupy myślicieli ośmiela się odwiedzić podziemia, gdzie robotnicy wykonują trudną pracę. Jest bardzo zdziwiony tym, co zobaczył..."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Metropolis","runtime":0,"tagline":"A kéz és az agy között nem lehet megértés, kivéve, ha a szív mediátorként működik.","homepage":"","overview":"John Masterman gigantikus Metropolisában csupán egy kiváltságos réteg élvezi a technikai fejlődés nyújtotta előnyöket. Számukra csodálatos kertek és ligetek kapui állnak nyitva, ők fényben és ragyogásban élnek. A város alsó szintjén tengődnek a szegények, a munkások, akik napfényt sose látnak, mesterségesen megvilágított körülmények között robotolnak naphosszat. A két szintet liftek kötik össze, egyébként lakóik között nincs semmi kapcsolat. Mígnem egy napon \"lentről\" érkezett gyerekcsapat zavarja meg a fentiek szórakozását, élükön a fiatal tanítónővel, Mariával. Ericet, Masterman fiát megszédíti a lány szépsége, és utána ered az alsó városba."},"name":"Magyar","iso_639_1":"hu","iso_3166_1":"HU","english_name":"Hungarian"},{"data":{"title":"Metropolis","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Gelecek zaman… İnsanlar iki gruba ayrılmış durumdadır: düşünenler (ancak hiçbir makinenin nasıl çalıştığını bilmiyorlar) ve çalışanlar (fikir sahibi değiller). Düşünenler planları yapıyor, çalışanlar da bunları uyguluyorlar. İki grup da tam değildir ama birleşince bir bütün oluyorlar. Bir gün düşünenlerden biri yeraltına çalışanların yanına iner. Gördükleriyle birlikte hayatın akışı değişmeye başlar…"},"name":"Türkçe","iso_639_1":"tr","iso_3166_1":"TR","english_name":"Turkish"},{"data":{"title":"Metropolis","runtime":150,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Metropolis kertoo tulevaisuuden suurkaupungista, jota hallitsee pieni onnelassaan elävä yläluokka teollisuuspohatta Johann Fredersenin johdolla. Kaupungin maanalaisissa uumenissa työläiset uurastavat valtavien koneiden keskellä ja konemaisiksi itsekin muuttuneina. Sorretut työläiset alkavat palvoa kaunista ja hyveellistä Mariaa, joka ennustaa rauhanomaista muutosta. Fredersenin poika ihastuu hänkin Mariaan. Pohatta itse päättää kidnapata Marian ja korvata tämän hullun tiedemiehen rakentamalla robotti-Marialla. Fritz Langin mestariteos oli valtava hanke. Se oli ensimmäinen suuren budjetin scifi-elokuva ja sen kuvaukset kestivät 16 kuukautta, ja niissä käytettiin 37 383 näyttelijää ja statistia. Eugen Schüftanin luomat erikoistehosteet ja ohjaaja Langin visiot tulevaisuuden suurkaupungista olivat ennennäkemättömiä. Metropoliksesta tuli siihen asti kallein saksalainen elokuva mutta myös valtava taloudellinen floppi, joka ajoi suuren Ufa-studion lähes konkurssiin."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Μετρόπολις","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Στο μέλλον, η τρανή πόλη «Μητρόπολη» είναι το καμάρι του σύγχρονου κόσμου, με κυβερνήτη τον Τζο Φρέντερσεν. Αυτή η πανέμορφη ουτοπία όμως δεν κινείται μόνη της. Είναι ένας καλο-λαδωμένος μηχανισμός, που λειτουργεί νύχτα-μέρα από τον εξαντλητικό κόπο και μόχθο των εργατών. Ομως, αυτή η κατάσταση, με τους αστούς να χαίρονται τη ζωή που τους προσφέρει ο μόχθος των εργατών, σύντομα θα αλλάξει, όταν ο γιος του Φρέντερσεν, ο Φρέντερ, που ζει μια ξένοιαστη ζωή γεμάτη γλέντια, γνωρίζει κατά τύχη την όμορφη Μαρία, κόρη ενός εργάτη..."},"name":"ελληνικά","iso_639_1":"el","iso_3166_1":"GR","english_name":"Greek"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Píše se rok 2026...vítejte v Metropolis. Vítejte ve studeném a přetechnizovaném městě budocnosti, ve světě vynálezů a prosperity, ale také sociálního útisku... Masy dělníků totiž žijí pod zemí a obsluhují stroje,aby smetánka na povrchu mohla bezstarostně žít...FREDER FREDERSEN (GUSTAV FRÖHLICH), syn vládce Metropolis, si užívá bezstarostně života v zahradách rozkoše, až do té doby, než se setká s MARIÍ (BRIGITTE HELM), kázající v podzemí dělníkům o lepším světě a interpretující jim starou biblickou pověst, zaměřenou na konflikt mezi vládnoucí a pracující třídou a vyzývá je ke vzpouře."},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"메트로폴리스","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"풍요로운 삶을 누리는 지상세계의 프레더는 어느날 마리아를 통해 지하 세계의 비참한 생활상을 알게된다. 프레더는 그의 아버지 프레드슨에게 노동자들의 삶을 개선해 줄 것을 요청하지만 거절당한다. 한편 마리아가 주도하는 지하 세계의 집회를 목격한 프레드슨은 로트왕에게 마리아와 똑같은 로봇을 만들어 지하세계의 노동자들을 교란할 것을 명령하는데..."},"name":"한국어/조선말","iso_639_1":"ko","iso_3166_1":"KR","english_name":"Korean"},{"data":{"title":"メトロポリス","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"科学の飛躍的な発展の結果、労働者たちは地下に押しやられ、巨大な工場で家畜同然に管理されている一方、資本家たちは地上で享楽的生活を送っている。社長の息子は地下に降りて、彼らの悲惨な生活を知る。労働者の娘マリアは、労使間に人間的な絆が皆無であることを仲間に訴え、これがストライキの気運を生む。そこで社長はマリアを監禁、彼女そっくりの人造人間を作って事態収拾にあたるが、人造人間は狂い始める。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":119,"tagline":"Fritz Langs mesterlige fremtidsvision.","homepage":"","overview":"Metropolis tegner en fremtid, hvor skellene mellem de forskellige klasser i samfundet er trukket skarpt op. Tænkerne bor højt oppe i højhusene, der udgør den flotte by. Arbejderne bor i katakomber under byen og må hver dag knokle i en stor fabrik under umenneskelige kår. Freder Fredersen er søn af en af Metropolis' ledere og ser en dag en smuk arbejderpige, Maria, som vinder hans hjerte. Han følger efter hende og ser, hvor forfærdeligt arbejderne har det. Freder prøver at overtaler sin far til at forbedre arbejdernes vilkår, og Maria fortæller arbejderne, at der en dag vil komme en mand, som både bruger sine hænder og sin hjerne, og han vil være hjertet. En gal professor laver en robot med Marias udseende, og der begynder at opstå revner i Metropolis' fine facade."},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Métropolis","runtime":153,"tagline":"Er kan geen begrip tussen de handen en het brein zijn zonder het hart als tussenpersoon","homepage":"","overview":"In een futuristische stad die duidelijk verdeeld is tussen de werkende klasse en de stadsarchitecten, wordt de zoon van de hoofdarchitect verliefd op een profeet uit de werkende klasse, die de komst van een redder voorspelt die in hun onenigheden zal bemiddelen."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"מטרופוליס","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"בעיר הדיסטופית מטרופוליס חיים הפועלים בתת-תנאים בעוד האליטה חיה במרומים. בעקבות התאהבותו, מצטרף צעיר בן מעמד האדונים למרד של העבדים. ואז מופיעה למאהבתו, מריה, כפילה רעה – רובוטית שנבנתה על ידי מדען מטורף על מנת להתסיס ולהוביל את המורדים אל כלייתם."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Metrópolis","runtime":123,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En una megalópolis del año 2000, los obreros están condenados a vivir recluidos en un gueto subterráneo, donde se encuentra el corazón industrial de la ciudad. Sin embargo, incitados por un robot, se rebelan contra la clase dominante y amenazan con destruir la ciudad exterior. Freder (Gustav Frölich), el hijo del soberano de Metrópolis, y María, una muchacha de origen humilde, intentarán evitar la destrucción apelando a los sentimientos y al amor."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Metrópolis","runtime":153,"tagline":"Não pode haver compreensão entre as mãos e o cérebro, a menos que o coração atue como mediador.","homepage":"","overview":"O futuro ė distante e o mundo está sob o comando dos poderosos, que isolaram os mais pobres no subsolo como se fossem seus escravos, para que trabalhassem em prol dos mesmos. Comandados por Freder Fredersen, os operários são obrigados a trabalharem sem parar para que a cidade não pare."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Метрополіс","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Художній фільм Фріца Ланґа за сценарієм і паралельно написаним романом Теа Фон Гарбоу. Це масштабна метафорична й науково-фантастична антиутопія, що стала найвищою сходинкою і завершенням розвитку німецького кiно-експресіонiзму. Фільм став безперечною класикою й вплинув на весь наступний розвиток кіномистецтва.  Метрополіс – місто майбутнього, яке поділене на 2 рівні. Під землею знаходяться житла робітників, а над ними цехи з машинами. У верхньому місті знаходяться офіси, багаті квартали і сади розваг. Уся влада в місті належить магнату Йо Фредерсену. Його син, Фредер, здогадується про несправедливість, яка панує в Метрополісі. Спустившись в машинну зону, Фредер жахається побаченого. Не маючи сили змиритися з тим, що відбувається, він починає боротьбу зі злом."},"name":"Український","iso_639_1":"uk","iso_3166_1":"UA","english_name":"Ukrainian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":149,"tagline":"Nu poate fi nicio înțelegere între mâini și creier fără ca inima să acționeze ca mediator.","homepage":"","overview":"Într-un oraș viitoresc împărțit strâns între clasa muncitoare și planificatorii orașului, fiul gânditorului orașului se îndrăgostește de o profetă a clasei muncitoare care prezice venirea unui salvator pentru a le media diferențele."},"name":"Română","iso_639_1":"ro","iso_3166_1":"RO","english_name":"Romanian"},{"data":{"title":"Метрополис","runtime":154,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Не може ума и ръцете да бъдат едно, освен ако сърцето не им е посредник. В едно фантастично бъдеще Работещите се изправят срещу Мислещите, за да открият, че биха могли да вървят напред единствено ако са заедно."},"name":"български език","iso_639_1":"bg","iso_3166_1":"BG","english_name":"Bulgarian"},{"data":{"title":"大都會","runtime":147,"tagline":"Metropolis","homepage":"","overview":"故事設置在2026年，電影完成的100年後，人類被分為兩個階層，生活在兩個截然不同的世界——權貴和富人都住在夢幻般的富麗大廈裡，每天過著享樂的生活；而貧窮的工薪階層則長期被困在幽暗的地下城市，與冰冷的機器相伴，過著勞碌辛苦的人生。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Metropolis","runtime":153,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"V roku 2027 prepukajú v meste budúcnosti nepokoje medzi nespokojnými robotníkmi a bohatou vrstvou žijúcej si na výslní. Freder, syn vládcu mesta, na vlastnej koži spoznáva neľudské podmienky, na ktorých mesto jeho otca stojí, a prepadne láske k Márii, prednášajúcej robotníkom o lepšom svete. Zanikne mesto tak, ako bájna babylonská veža, alebo dôjde k zmieru?"},"name":"Slovenčina","iso_639_1":"sk","iso_3166_1":"SK","english_name":"Slovak"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"لا يمكن أن يكون هناك تفاهم بين اليدين والدماغ إلا إذا عمل القلب كوسيط.","homepage":"","overview":"في مدينة مستقبلية منقسمة بحدة بين الطبقة العاملة ومخططي المدينة ، يقع ابن العقل المدبر للمدينة في حب نبي من الطبقة العاملة يتنبأ بمجيء المنقذ للتوسط في خلافاتهم."},"name":"العربية","iso_639_1":"ar","iso_3166_1":"SA","english_name":"Arabic"},{"data":{"title":"Metropole","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"},{"data":{"title":"เมโทรโพลิส เมืองล่าหุ่นยนต์","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ในเมืองแห่งอนาคตที่มีการแบ่งแยกอย่างชัดเจนระหว่างคนรวยและคนจน ลูกชายของผู้วางแผนหลักในเมืองได้พบกับศาสดาผู้ทำนายการมาถึงของพระผู้ช่วยให้รอดเพื่อไกล่เกลี่ยความแตกต่างระหว่างพวกเขา"},"name":"ภาษาไทย","iso_639_1":"th","iso_3166_1":"TH","english_name":"Thai"},{"data":{"title":"Metròpolis","runtime":0,"tagline":"No hi pot haver acord entre les mans i el cervell llevat que el cor actuï com a mediador.","homepage":"","overview":"En una megalòpolis de l'any 2000, els obrers estan condemnats a viure reclosos en un gueto subterrani, on hi ha el cor industrial de la ciutat. No obstant això, incitats per un robot, es rebel·len contra la classe dominant i amenacen de destruir la ciutat exterior. Freder (Gustav Frölich), el fill del sobirà de Metròpolis, i Maria, una noia d'origen humil, intentaran evitar la destrucció apel·lant als sentiments ia l'amor."},"name":"Català","iso_639_1":"ca","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Catalan"},{"data":{"title":"大都會","runtime":147,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"故事設置在 2026 年，電影完成的 100 年後，人類被分為兩個階層，生活在兩個截然不同的世界——權貴和富人都住在夢幻般的富麗大廈裡，每天過著享樂的生活；而貧窮的工薪階層則長期被困在幽暗的地下城市，與冰冷的機器相伴，過著勞碌辛苦的人生。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"HK","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":163,"tagline":"Il ne peut y avoir de compréhension entre les mains et le cerveau que si le cœur agit comme médiateur.","homepage":"","overview":"En 2026, une métropole à l’architecture fantastique vit sous le joug d’un groupe de tyrans. Les aristocrates se prélassent et se divertissent dans de somptueuses demeures et de luxuriants jardins, tandis que la grande masse de la population travaille, dort et survit durement dans les profondeurs de la terre. Le fils du maître de la ville découvre avec effarement l’existence du monde souterrain, où se rencontrent en secret les ouvriers, peu enclins à supporter pour toujours leur situation. Pendant ce temps, un savant invente une femme‐robot qui doit détourner les opprimés de leur révolte…"},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"CA","english_name":"French"}],"reviews_tmdb":[{"id":"538a4cc10e0a2605eb0007cf","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/538a4cc10e0a2605eb0007cf","author":"Gurre","content":"$11","created_at":"2014-05-31T21:42:25.543Z","updated_at":"2021-06-23T15:57:26.631Z","author_details":{"name":"","rating":10,"username":"Gurre","avatar_path":null}},{"id":"629e4643dc1cb452e0018a34","url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/review/629e4643dc1cb452e0018a34","author":"CinemaSerf","content":"$12","created_at":"2022-06-06T18:24:03.310Z","updated_at":"2022-06-06T18:24:03.310Z","author_details":{"name":"CinemaSerf","rating":8,"username":"Geronimo1967","avatar_path":"/9HcQx0Yfbxy8eqr3ft66X9uWMf0.jpg"}}],"recommendations":[{"id":832,"adult":false,"title":"M","video":false,"overview":"In this classic German thriller, Hans Beckert, a serial killer who preys on children, becomes the focus of a massive Berlin police manhunt. Beckert's heinous crimes are so repellant and disruptive to city life that he is even targeted by others in the seedy underworld network. With both cops and criminals in pursuit, the murderer soon realizes that people are on his trail, sending him into a tense, panicked attempt to escape justice.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0856,"vote_count":2414,"poster_path":"/bTdZk3q2DWpBRnLiaaItKFWOVhI.jpg","release_date":"1931-05-11","vote_average":8.063,"backdrop_path":"/5Pk1rGAtyblh9Xaq72T7ARCQSDQ.jpg","original_title":"M - Eine Stadt sucht einen Mörder","original_language":"de"},{"id":9606,"adult":false,"title":"Metropolis","video":false,"overview":"In the midst of societal conflict in the futuristic city of Metropolis, Kenichi and his uncle Shunsaku Ban set out to uncover the mystery behind the first human-like robot, Tima.","genre_ids":[16,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.8414,"vote_count":542,"poster_path":"/41WtqvaObaYE3RuqgBfQFPV3aV1.jpg","release_date":"2001-05-26","vote_average":7.152,"backdrop_path":"/nDXRRMYubyKqudMGAq0Ro0hd7lA.jpg","original_title":"メトロポリス","original_language":"ja"},{"id":2760,"adult":false,"title":"The Lodger: A Story of the London Fog","video":false,"overview":"London. A mysterious serial killer brutally murders young blond women by stalking them in the night fog. One foggy, sinister night, a young man who claims his name is Jonathan Drew arrives at the guest house run by the Bunting family and rents a room.","genre_ids":[80,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7646,"vote_count":326,"poster_path":"/tD84zwFeFRf3zG98x558N3PBMV.jpg","release_date":"1927-02-14","vote_average":7.1,"backdrop_path":"/8svHeSlKssWjscBaa2HnFZR9oo4.jpg","original_title":"The Lodger: A Story of the London Fog","original_language":"en"},{"id":631,"adult":false,"title":"Sunrise: A Song of Two Humans","video":false,"overview":"A married farmer falls under the spell of a slatternly woman from the city, who tries to convince him to drown his wife.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8102,"vote_count":880,"poster_path":"/oj8ZW8jKXBSs8F1e5iWsTUeXSJW.jpg","release_date":"1927-11-04","vote_average":7.818,"backdrop_path":"/hKrrCigPFmhv1bg5IJl9nzjEaN4.jpg","original_title":"Sunrise: A Song of Two Humans","original_language":"en"},{"id":653,"adult":false,"title":"Nosferatu","video":false,"overview":"The mysterious Count Orlok summons a happily married real estate agent to his castle, located up in the Transylvanian mountains, to finalise a terrifying deal.","genre_ids":[27,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.2842,"vote_count":2396,"poster_path":"/zv7J85D8CC9qYagAEhPM63CIG6j.jpg","release_date":"1922-02-16","vote_average":7.7,"backdrop_path":"/u06SympEEMb7pLhR9W3tvydHT9L.jpg","original_title":"Nosferatu, eine Symphonie des Grauens","original_language":"de"},{"id":697,"adult":false,"title":"October (Ten Days that Shook the World)","video":false,"overview":"Sergei M. Eisenstein's docu-drama about the 1917 October Revolution in Russia. Made ten years after the events and edited in Eisenstein's 'Soviet Montage' style, it re-enacts in celebratory terms several key scenes from the revolution.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.5514,"vote_count":217,"poster_path":"/2sNZPybGgux2keFKxZuKuedrS3d.jpg","release_date":"1928-05-11","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/quCVnWjPoFfxsHL0vQTewwPLhxa.jpg","original_title":"Октябрь","original_language":"ru"},{"id":939,"adult":false,"title":"The Jazz Singer","video":false,"overview":"A young Jewish man is torn between tradition and individuality when his old-fashioned family objects to his career as a jazz singer. This is the first full length feature film to use synchronized sound, and is the original film musical.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9699,"vote_count":245,"poster_path":"/wr8Pt1GO87cwB3210TO3JTNDsUc.jpg","release_date":"1927-10-06","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/515FMUnY7irFM0zsMKPvclMUUnJ.jpg","original_title":"The Jazz Singer","original_language":"en"},{"id":3007,"adult":false,"title":"Woman in the Moon","video":false,"overview":"A scientist discovers that there's gold on the moon. He builds a rocket to fly there, but there's too much rivalry among the crew to have a successful expedition.","genre_ids":[18,878,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6539,"vote_count":112,"poster_path":"/7s6zEsOAY3LD5qvzljmKKzjnLiT.jpg","release_date":"1929-10-15","vote_average":7.25,"backdrop_path":"/cvAOkB5bryGWbxp8SqD1ovEsF4v.jpg","original_title":"Frau im Mond","original_language":"de"},{"id":82283,"adult":false,"title":"It","video":false,"overview":"A flapper shopgirl woos her rich boss with animal magnetism -- the captivating personal quality otherwise known as \"it.\"","genre_ids":[35,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6196,"vote_count":72,"poster_path":"/nkkhsKik9GILqn3S5BxoZdyml21.jpg","release_date":"1927-02-05","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/ygMZ9DamhPIgQOT5WjacsfvPXIX.jpg","original_title":"It","original_language":"en"},{"id":234,"adult":false,"title":"The Cabinet of Dr. Caligari","video":false,"overview":"Francis, a young man, recalls in his memory the horrible experiences he and his fiancée Jane recently went through. Francis and his friend Alan visit The Cabinet of Dr. Caligari, an exhibit where the mysterious doctor shows the somnambulist Cesare, and awakens him for some moments from his death-like sleep.","genre_ids":[18,27,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9484,"vote_count":1730,"poster_path":"/myK9DeIsXWGKgUTZyGXg2IfFk0W.jpg","release_date":"1920-02-27","vote_average":7.933,"backdrop_path":"/iNNNkYuUU365LhnPwQqfzBvKnsg.jpg","original_title":"Das Cabinet des Dr. Caligari","original_language":"de"},{"id":626,"adult":false,"title":"Un Chien Andalou","video":false,"overview":"Un Chien Andalou is an European avant-garde surrealist film, a collaboration between director Luis Buñuel and Salvador Dali.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2886,"vote_count":1389,"poster_path":"/obvE7ElAvCUhKtWFwDSvNbPw9PV.jpg","release_date":"1929-06-05","vote_average":7.397,"backdrop_path":"/jQywhaFDVLPlFw864Bgw5eNtWfi.jpg","original_title":"Un chien andalou","original_language":"fr"},{"id":490,"adult":false,"title":"The Seventh Seal","video":false,"overview":"When disillusioned Swedish knight Antonius Block returns home from the Crusades to find his country in the grips of the Black Death, he challenges Death to a chess match for his life. Tormented by the belief that God does not exist, Block sets off on a journey, meeting up with traveling players Jof and his wife, Mia, and becoming determined to evade Death long enough to commit one redemptive act while he still lives.","genre_ids":[14,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.6708,"vote_count":3278,"poster_path":"/wcZ21zrOsy0b52AfAF50XpTiv75.jpg","release_date":"1957-02-16","vote_average":8.164,"backdrop_path":"/6s2BqtDvp1BMiP70zCDU5OW6hMy.jpg","original_title":"Det sjunde inseglet","original_language":"sv"},{"id":901,"adult":false,"title":"City Lights","video":false,"overview":"A tramp falls in love with a beautiful blind flower girl. His on-and-off friendship with a wealthy man allows him to be the girl's benefactor and suitor.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.9439,"vote_count":2398,"poster_path":"/bXNvzjULc9jrOVhGfjcc64uKZmZ.jpg","release_date":"1931-02-06","vote_average":8.258,"backdrop_path":"/aSksN0VqrRyXkcJPDqGL6S3gxpl.jpg","original_title":"City Lights","original_language":"en"},{"id":15,"adult":false,"title":"Citizen Kane","video":false,"overview":"Newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane is taken from his mother as a boy and made the ward of a rich industrialist. As a result, every well-meaning, tyrannical or self-destructive move he makes for the rest of his life appears in some way to be a reaction to that deeply wounding event.","genre_ids":[9648,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.0189,"vote_count":5936,"poster_path":"/sav0jxhqiH0bPr2vZFU0Kjt2nZL.jpg","release_date":"1941-04-17","vote_average":7.98,"backdrop_path":"/9Y85oA1y6toL2OACXdaC6iTl7eQ.jpg","original_title":"Citizen Kane","original_language":"en"},{"id":26317,"adult":false,"title":"Man with a Movie Camera","video":false,"overview":"A cameraman wanders around with a camera slung over his shoulder, documenting urban life with dazzling inventiveness.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9854,"vote_count":785,"poster_path":"/vJgAdgJWX54v0oXfIvhwjlZnmgn.jpg","release_date":"1929-05-12","vote_average":7.835,"backdrop_path":"/byRNEm1QwfQC1Mn0K4gLM2fIfWO.jpg","original_title":"Человек с киноаппаратом","original_language":"ru"},{"id":780,"adult":false,"title":"The Passion of Joan of Arc","video":false,"overview":"A classic of the silent age, this film tells the story of the doomed but ultimately canonized 15th-century teenage warrior. On trial for claiming she'd spoken to God, Jeanne d'Arc is subjected to inhumane treatment and scare tactics at the hands of church court officials. Initially bullied into changing her story, Jeanne eventually opts for what she sees as the truth. Her punishment, a famously brutal execution, earns her perpetual martyrdom.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5913,"vote_count":1062,"poster_path":"/tAgV9yxY6AC1bsPt3qJJQpD4s8.jpg","release_date":"1928-04-21","vote_average":7.981,"backdrop_path":"/cFgCf2XqnhErS3HmgSOBCe4kL4d.jpg","original_title":"La Passion de Jeanne d'Arc","original_language":"fr"},{"id":614,"adult":false,"title":"Wild Strawberries","video":false,"overview":"Crotchety retired doctor Isak Borg travels from Stockholm to Lund, Sweden, with his pregnant and unhappy daughter-in-law, Marianne, in order to receive an honorary degree from his alma mater. Along the way, they encounter a series of hitchhikers, each of whom causes the elderly doctor to muse upon the pleasures and failures of his own life. These include the vivacious young Sara, a dead ringer for the doctor's own first love.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9723,"vote_count":1772,"poster_path":"/iyTD2QnySNMPUPE3IedZQipSWfz.jpg","release_date":"1957-08-28","vote_average":8.087,"backdrop_path":"/BBVAUchYvkmPThVIqipgAfabfl.jpg","original_title":"Smultronstället","original_language":"sv"},{"id":11549,"adult":false,"title":"Invasion of the Body Snatchers","video":false,"overview":"A small-town doctor learns that the population of his community is being replaced by emotionless alien duplicates.","genre_ids":[878,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4382,"vote_count":1168,"poster_path":"/8BrMQmgwGzIHSyBjCDOLOdi79fJ.jpg","release_date":"1956-02-05","vote_average":7.458,"backdrop_path":"/qcLHMO01oECjbL8MUPRXsLOMFhx.jpg","original_title":"Invasion of the Body Snatchers","original_language":"en"},{"id":895,"adult":false,"title":"Andrei Rublev","video":false,"overview":"An expansive Russian drama, this film focuses on the life of revered religious icon painter Andrei Rublev. Drifting from place to place in a tumultuous era, the peace-seeking monk eventually gains a reputation for his art. But after Rublev witnesses a brutal battle and unintentionally becomes involved, he takes a vow of silence and spends time away from his work. As he begins to ease his troubled soul, he takes steps towards becoming a painter once again.","genre_ids":[18,36],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.5524,"vote_count":922,"poster_path":"/910xRIUmNJrWH2hkQifBJtoPp5R.jpg","release_date":"1966-12-16","vote_average":7.967,"backdrop_path":"/jqha8JCXm0aJ5SJ03Jd0JmGgWRs.jpg","original_title":"Андрей Рублёв","original_language":"ru"},{"id":1040,"adult":false,"title":"The Leopard","video":false,"overview":"As Garibaldi's troops begin the unification of Italy in the 1860s, an aristocratic Sicilian family grudgingly adapts to the sweeping social changes undermining their way of life. Proud but pragmatic Prince Don Fabrizio Salina allows his war hero nephew, Tancredi, to marry Angelica, the beautiful daughter of gauche, bourgeois Don Calogero, in order to maintain the family's accustomed level of comfort and political clout.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.9919,"vote_count":924,"poster_path":"/riSUxwoK3xjkOgy6YJSvPhi7cO6.jpg","release_date":"1963-03-27","vote_average":7.716,"backdrop_path":"/myikoqu8Z2gtE7TaBgk9r6fB9MF.jpg","original_title":"Il gattopardo","original_language":"it"}],"similar_content":[{"id":463012,"adult":false,"title":"Albert Savarus","video":false,"overview":"Adaptation of the Balzac story as told by Rosalie, a young girl in love with the idea of her extraordinary neighbor, Albert Savarus, and the lengths she goes to ensure their marriage, even after she learns he is deeply in love with another woman.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.192,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/h3h6qNQTJAxGJKSEf17UgiPi3LO.jpg","release_date":"1993-01-30","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/z6T8aLoNNFalUIuaw6Yr0a443DK.jpg","original_title":"Albert Savarus","original_language":"fr"},{"id":93,"adult":false,"title":"Anatomy of a Murder","video":false,"overview":"Semi-retired Michigan lawyer Paul Biegler takes the case of Army Lt. Manion, who murdered a local innkeeper after his wife claimed that he raped her. Over the course of an extensive trial, Biegler parries with District Attorney Lodwick and out-of-town prosecutor Claude Dancer to set his client free, but his case rests on the victim's mysterious business partner, who's hiding a dark secret.","genre_ids":[80,18,9648],"popularity":2.1998,"vote_count":1125,"poster_path":"/b2G1QSAwtBv9luhEwErIgSRaU92.jpg","release_date":"1959-07-01","vote_average":7.836,"backdrop_path":"/xfEU7DOlQPwz8Y0TBhKmpETuNIc.jpg","original_title":"Anatomy of a Murder","original_language":"en"},{"id":97,"adult":false,"title":"Tron","video":false,"overview":"When brilliant video game maker Flynn hacks the mainframe of his ex-employer, he is beamed inside an astonishing digital world and becomes part of the very game he is designing. In his mission through cyberspace, Flynn matches wits with a maniacal Master Control Program and teams up with Tron, a security measure created to bring balance to the digital environment.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":5.4942,"vote_count":2659,"poster_path":"/jigY9B6TKz4qlfikZcd18qtzTK4.jpg","release_date":"1982-07-09","vote_average":6.636,"backdrop_path":"/vUmeBHiGp5r2ydd8aEvbNLamTVD.jpg","original_title":"Tron","original_language":"en"},{"id":103,"adult":false,"title":"Taxi Driver","video":false,"overview":"Suffering from insomnia, disturbed loner Travis Bickle takes a job as a New York City cabbie, haunting the streets nightly, growing increasingly detached from reality as he dreams of cleaning up the filthy city.","genre_ids":[80,18],"popularity":13.6161,"vote_count":13209,"poster_path":"/ekstpH614fwDX8DUln1a2Opz0N8.jpg","release_date":"1976-02-09","vote_average":8.128,"backdrop_path":"/9uddYYTNcLWpzUkl5iw1RUYhLhY.jpg","original_title":"Taxi Driver","original_language":"en"},{"id":105,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future","video":false,"overview":"Eighties teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent back in time to 1955, inadvertently disrupting his parents' first meeting and attracting his mother's romantic interest. Marty must repair the damage to history by rekindling his parents' romance and - with the help of his eccentric inventor friend Doc Brown - return to 1985.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"popularity":18.3599,"vote_count":21417,"poster_path":"/vN5B5WgYscRGcQpVhHl6p9DDTP0.jpg","release_date":"1985-07-03","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/qskzmLTbarKnXDbo2HRj4NJ3vcW.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future","original_language":"en"},{"id":15,"adult":false,"title":"Citizen Kane","video":false,"overview":"Newspaper magnate Charles Foster Kane is taken from his mother as a boy and made the ward of a rich industrialist. As a result, every well-meaning, tyrannical or self-destructive move he makes for the rest of his life appears in some way to be a reaction to that deeply wounding event.","genre_ids":[9648,18],"popularity":6.0189,"vote_count":5936,"poster_path":"/sav0jxhqiH0bPr2vZFU0Kjt2nZL.jpg","release_date":"1941-04-17","vote_average":7.98,"backdrop_path":"/9Y85oA1y6toL2OACXdaC6iTl7eQ.jpg","original_title":"Citizen Kane","original_language":"en"},{"id":18,"adult":false,"title":"The Fifth Element","video":false,"overview":"In 2257, a taxi driver is unintentionally given the task of saving a young girl who is part of the key that will ensure the survival of humanity.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":11.8876,"vote_count":11464,"poster_path":"/fPtlCO1yQtnoLHOwKtWz7db6RGU.jpg","release_date":"1997-05-02","vote_average":7.6,"backdrop_path":"/bx1W729hyWQqNQoiq9LsX30FBf.jpg","original_title":"Le Cinquième Élément","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1252309,"adult":false,"title":"Tell Me What You Want","video":false,"overview":"After his father's death, Eric Zimmerman travels to Spain to oversee his company's branches. In Madrid, he falls for Judith and engage in an intense, erotic relationship full of exploration. However, Eric fears his secret may end their affair.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":12.7566,"vote_count":268,"poster_path":"/yZXYCiZQPB7Ui6D5206W1zDKv8P.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-29","vote_average":6.131,"backdrop_path":"/8Rseq6hAhAItnTrbECEFt35VoSJ.jpg","original_title":"Pídeme lo que quieras","original_language":"es"},{"id":271297,"adult":false,"title":"That Eye, the Sky","video":false,"overview":"Ort Flack is 12 years old and lives with his mother and his sister Tegwyn in the Australian outback. The three of them also have to take care of their old grandma and their paralyzed father. It is not easy for one mother to take care of everybody. But one day a mysterious stranger, Henry, comes to their desolate house to help them...","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.2017,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/u1yc7CbO3xWg4NIBCCncWmqYAqc.jpg","release_date":"1995-09-28","vote_average":3.75,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"That Eye, the Sky","original_language":"en"},{"id":28,"adult":false,"title":"Apocalypse Now","video":false,"overview":"At the height of the Vietnam war, Captain Benjamin Willard is sent on a dangerous mission that, officially, \"does not exist, nor will it ever exist.\" His goal is to locate - and eliminate - a mysterious Green Beret Colonel named Walter Kurtz, who has been leading his personal army on illegal guerrilla missions into enemy territory.","genre_ids":[18,10752],"popularity":12.0335,"vote_count":8894,"poster_path":"/gQB8Y5RCMkv2zwzFHbUJX3kAhvA.jpg","release_date":"1979-05-19","vote_average":8.267,"backdrop_path":"/eN5G8vTWLnZxJ0LTd4g27oPObcZ.jpg","original_title":"Apocalypse Now","original_language":"en"},{"id":62,"adult":false,"title":"2001: A Space Odyssey","video":false,"overview":"Humanity finds a mysterious object buried beneath the lunar surface and sets off to find its origins with the help of HAL 9000, the world's most advanced super computer.","genre_ids":[878,9648,12],"popularity":11.9001,"vote_count":12360,"poster_path":"/ve72VxNqjGM69Uky4WTo2bK6rfq.jpg","release_date":"1968-04-02","vote_average":8.057,"backdrop_path":"/w5IDXtifKntw0ajv2co7jFlTQDM.jpg","original_title":"2001: A Space Odyssey","original_language":"en"},{"id":63,"adult":false,"title":"Twelve Monkeys","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2035, convict James Cole reluctantly volunteers to be sent back in time to discover the origin of a deadly virus that wiped out nearly all of the earth's population and forced the survivors into underground communities. But when Cole is mistakenly sent to 1990 instead of 1996, he's arrested and locked up in a mental hospital. There he meets psychiatrist Dr. Kathryn Railly and the son of a famous virus expert who may hold the key to the Army of the 12 Monkeys; thought to be responsible for unleashing the killer disease.","genre_ids":[878,53,9648],"popularity":8.5281,"vote_count":8939,"poster_path":"/gt3iyguaCIw8DpQZI1LIN5TohM2.jpg","release_date":"1995-12-29","vote_average":7.601,"backdrop_path":"/mKIkGoyuR71qz6FdiEiOjxvBQcS.jpg","original_title":"Twelve Monkeys","original_language":"en"},{"id":66,"adult":false,"title":"Absolute Power","video":false,"overview":"A master thief coincidentally is robbing a house where a murder—in which the President of the United States is involved—occurs in front of his eyes. He is forced to run, while holding evidence that could convict the President.","genre_ids":[80,18,28],"popularity":2.7585,"vote_count":1202,"poster_path":"/izvyt3cxlilhbYwybTOteDWqf99.jpg","release_date":"1997-02-14","vote_average":6.658,"backdrop_path":"/cLftTzGw40BlLw8IggKSWDjKOQo.jpg","original_title":"Absolute Power","original_language":"en"},{"id":271359,"adult":false,"title":"Suzanna","video":false,"overview":"Hoping to consolidate their adjoining ranches, Don Fernando and Don Diego betroth their children, Ramón and Dolores, although Ramón is in love with Suzanna, the daughter of a peon on his father's ranch, and Dolores is interested in Pancho, a toreador. When Suzanna learns that she was kidnapped in infancy and is really Don Diego's daughter, she keeps silent; but Ramón finally rebels and steals Suzanna from the altar as she is about to marry Pancho. There are explanations, Ramón marries Suzanna, and Dolores marries Pancho. Suzanna (1923) has been mastered from a good quality but incomplete 35mm print.","genre_ids":[10749,18],"popularity":0.1777,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/cqHVIZ5BIU1ZHIxce0fNwsCAJ0V.jpg","release_date":"1923-02-16","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Suzanna","original_language":"en"},{"id":271373,"adult":false,"title":"The Abandoned Documents of a Dead Woman","video":false,"overview":"Based on the novel by Güzide Sabri, the film tells the story of a woman suffering from a forbidden love.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.132,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/4pRq4XcqkiuxjUmBD9TcjK7nZ9D.jpg","release_date":"1956-01-01","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Ölmüş Bir Kadının Evrak-ı Metrukesi","original_language":"tr"},{"id":68,"adult":false,"title":"Brazil","video":false,"overview":"Low-level bureaucrat Sam Lowry escapes the monotony of his day-to-day life through a recurring daydream of himself as a virtuous hero saving a beautiful damsel. Investigating a case that led to the wrongful arrest and eventual death of an innocent man instead of wanted terrorist Harry Tuttle, he meets the woman from his daydream, and in trying to help her gets caught in a web of mistaken identities, mindless bureaucracy and lies.","genre_ids":[35,878],"popularity":3.6643,"vote_count":3611,"poster_path":"/aewan59WcFThBimkTVVoNf2o5Vb.jpg","release_date":"1985-02-20","vote_average":7.666,"backdrop_path":"/9IYyCLf5NNAQFK9pNtqzEU9HWzM.jpg","original_title":"Brazil","original_language":"en"},{"id":74,"adult":false,"title":"War of the Worlds","video":false,"overview":"Ray Ferrier is a divorced dockworker and less-than-perfect father. Soon after his ex-wife and her new husband drop off his teenage son and young daughter for a rare weekend visit, a strange and powerful lightning storm touches down.","genre_ids":[12,53,878],"popularity":8.8816,"vote_count":8977,"poster_path":"/6Biy7R9LfumYshur3YKhpj56MpB.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-28","vote_average":6.531,"backdrop_path":"/bInicBgSHfQiWLbnRT5jxw9Grvm.jpg","original_title":"War of the Worlds","original_language":"en"},{"id":78,"adult":false,"title":"Blade Runner","video":false,"overview":"In the smog-choked dystopian Los Angeles of 2019, blade runner Rick Deckard is called out of retirement to terminate a quartet of replicants who have escaped to Earth seeking their creator for a way to extend their short life spans.","genre_ids":[878,18,53],"popularity":11.9762,"vote_count":14713,"poster_path":"/63N9uy8nd9j7Eog2axPQ8lbr3Wj.jpg","release_date":"1982-06-25","vote_average":7.94,"backdrop_path":"/hJ5R9d6QuH3tzr8L8neZZTuzNXm.jpg","original_title":"Blade Runner","original_language":"en"},{"id":86,"adult":false,"title":"The Elementary Particles","video":false,"overview":"Based on Michel Houellebecq's controversial novel, Atomised (aka The Elementary Particles) focuses on Michael and Bruno, two very different half-brothers and their disturbed sexuality.  After a chaotic childhood with a hippie mother only caring for her affairs, Michael, a molecular biologist, is more interested in genes than women, while Bruno is obsessed with his sexual desires, but mostly finds his satisfaction with prostitutes.  But Bruno's life changes when he gets to know the experienced Christiane.  In the meantime, Michael meets Annabelle, the love of his youth, again.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"popularity":0.6159,"vote_count":146,"poster_path":"/wpGpR7GewyApPgqPvuWadBAfmFc.jpg","release_date":"2006-02-10","vote_average":6.12,"backdrop_path":"/60PJPzXtQmLQdaCNuWUrrHe1mzu.jpg","original_title":"Elementarteilchen","original_language":"de"},{"id":653824,"adult":false,"title":"Casa din vis","video":false,"overview":"Căpălău, a peasant in a village near Brăila, tries to keep up with the turns of life. Based on \"Ningea în Bără